belongs_to_collection.name: Honto Ni Atta! Noroi no Video Collection

original_title: ほんとにあった! 呪いのビデオ 32
overview: A collection of horrifying psychic images submitted by general posts, "It was really there! Cursed video". Fear grows! Earth-bound spirits, grudges, floating spirits, guardian spirits ... Full of mysterious images that cannot be elucidated by science; including 'Sports day', 'Dog-walking', 'Club event', 'absence', 'Series surveillance camera Internet cafe refugee', 'taxi', 'Red person' and 'Twenty Seven Part 1'.
title: Honto ni Atta! Noroi no Video Vol. 32
